Adopt [[http://wiki.whatwg.org/wiki/Crypto|Adam Barth's proposal]] as a source of cryptographically strong random numbers, but with an API based on [[harmony:binary_data]], and made available (somehow) via the module system rather than introducing yet another property on the global object. [[https://bugs.webkit.org/show_bug.cgi?id=22049#c1|This comment]] explains one of the problems with simply adding this to the global object.


